Distribution. Europe, northern Africa ( Algeria ), Middle Asia, Siberia, Far East, China and Japan . Distribution in China : Heilongjiang, Hebei, Tianjin , Ningxia, Gansu, Xinjiang, Jiangsu, Hubei, Sichuan, Guizhou (
